if she thinks it's still working.

06:24.258 --> 06:27.261
<i> This is what I get</i>
<i>for trying to out-tech a teenager.</i>

06:27.470 --> 06:30.014
<i>It's a good thing I have another way</i>
<i>to keep tabs.</i>

06:36.521 --> 06:37.939
<i> Henderson's jacktop.</i>

06:39.565 --> 06:41.651
<i>Even if he's realized</i>
<i>it's gone missing by now,</i>

06:41.734 --> 06:43.486
