06:43.569 --> 06:46.072
<i>and he hasn't been diligent enough</i>
<i>to un-sync his IMs.</i>

06:54.747 --> 06:56.582
<i>Ellie hasn't fallen in line,</i>

06:56.666 --> 06:57.875
<i>she's gotten craftier.</i>

06:58.126 --> 07:01.254
<i>I could tell Delilah, but then</i>
<i>I'd have to explain how I know.</i>

07:10.847 --> 07:13.599
<i>Or I could take care of it.</i>

07:13.975 --> 07:15.977
<i>The brave, good, right thing to do,</i>

07:16.060 --> 07:17.937
<i>the kind of man you'd want me to be.</i>

07:20.940 --> 07:24.402
<i>People have secret rooms</i>
<i>to hide something shameful</i>

07:24.485 --> 07:26.028
<i>and doubtless, illegal.</i>

07:26.112 --> 07:27.655
<i>If I find what Hendy's hiding,</i>

07:27.864 --> 07:29.824
<i>I can get him arrested and Ellie safe.</i>

07:29.907 --> 07:31.033
<i>I'll make you proud.</i>

07:33.119 --> 07:36.831
<i>With Hendy out of town,</i>
<i>perfect time to get back inside his house.</i>

07:53.181 --> 07:56.309
<i>But first, there's someone else</i>
<i>I have to take care of.</i>

08:05.443 --> 08:06.277
Eat it up.

08:06.861 --> 08:10.156
I paid a lot
for those macrobiotic sea vegetables.

08:24.962 --> 08:26.047
Okay.

08:26.130 --> 08:27.131
Okay what?

08:27.215 --> 08:29.425
Okay, let's have the conversation.

08:30.009 --> 08:31.135
If I let you out...

08:31.928 --> 08:33.095
then what?

08:34.263 --> 08:35.389
Is this a joke?

08:36.140 --> 08:39.602
<i>No, the only joke is me pretending</i>
<i>that keeping a man in a cage</i>

08:39.685 --> 08:41.312
<i>is helping me be my best self.</i>

08:41.395 --> 08:42.313
No.

08:42.647 --> 08:43.940
What's your plan?

08:44.440 --> 08:46.067
My plan is...

08:46.859 --> 08:48.611
to forget any of this happened...

08:49.278 --> 08:52.490
and to live happily ever after
with Gigi in Manila.

08:53.199 --> 08:56.285
<i>Gigi, Will's internet fianc√©e,</i>

08:56.369 --> 08:59.121
<i>a.k.a. least promising plan of all time.</i>

08:59.330 --> 09:02.250
If you bring me the <i>Beast Wars</i> box
in my coat closet,

09:03.084 --> 09:05.169
