09:05.419 --> 09:07.380
and you will never hear from me again.

09:07.463 --> 09:08.464
I have an idea.

09:10.299 --> 09:11.342
You like games.

09:11.717 --> 09:14.720
Love 'em, in other contexts, dude.

09:14.804 --> 09:15.680
Right.

09:16.889 --> 09:17.974
I will let you out...

09:18.558 --> 09:19.433
if you prove

09:19.517 --> 09:21.269
you'll never turn me in.

09:23.062 --> 09:24.146
Prove my loyalty?

09:25.690 --> 09:28.776
And how am I supposed to do that
from inside a cage?

09:30.152 --> 09:32.363
I don't know. You're smart.
I believe in you.

09:35.491 --> 09:36.325
Don't give up.

09:36.909 --> 09:39.328
You need something
to get your brain juices flowing.

09:40.079 --> 09:41.372
You need a project.

09:45.209 --> 09:46.627
What do you need this time?

09:48.504 --> 09:50.965
I need Henderson's home security disabled.

09:51.048 --> 09:53.217
-He's hiding something.

09:53.301 --> 09:54.594
Sounds familiar.

09:58.431 --> 09:59.849
You're gonna need a jammer.

10:00.558 --> 10:02.018
Question is which kind,

10:02.101 --> 10:04.228
so I'll need to know what system he's got.

10:05.104 --> 10:07.648
Oh, am I allowed to touch a laptop

10:07.732 --> 10:09.108
to help you...

10:09.692 --> 10:11.611
help me help you do this thing?

10:18.034 --> 10:19.327
Stop. That one.

10:19.785 --> 10:21.203
Is that a sign by the hedge?

10:22.622 --> 10:25.583
People put those signs around their house
to make them feel safe

10:25.958 --> 10:27.918
because they are, respectfully,

10:28.544 --> 10:30.713
idiots of the highest magnitude.

10:31.255 --> 10:33.424
<i> 'Cause it only makes it easier</i>
<i>for people like me</i>

10:33.507 --> 10:35.718
<i>to find out which frequency</i>
<i>they're broadcasting on.</i>

10:35.801 --> 10:37.470
<i>Once you jam the frequency,</i>

10:37.553 --> 10:39.096
<i>all the sensors are disabled.</i>

10:57.740 --> 11:00.534
<i> Good ol' Hendy has obviously</i>
<i>never seen </i>The Bling Ring.

11:05.456 --> 11:08.042
<i>Okay, Hendy, where's the toy room?</i>

11:10.670 --> 11:13.047
