11:13.547 --> 11:15.383
<i>Oh, Mr. Tumnus.</i>

11:42.368 --> 11:43.327
<i>Huh.</i>

11:43.577 --> 11:45.830
<i>Wouldn't have pegged him</i>
<i>for a Dickens guy.</i>

11:49.458 --> 11:51.627
<i>Oh, how very supervillain-y.</i>

12:01.804 --> 12:05.516
<i>It's like Hendy's id</i>
<i>ate too much candy and porn</i>

12:05.599 --> 12:06.809
<i>and threw it all up.</i>

12:22.783 --> 12:26.078
<i> 'Cause nothing's worse</i>
<i>than a sex dungeon with dust bunnies.</i>

12:31.751 --> 12:33.252
<i>Could he be more obvious?</i>

