and it comes out later

21:14.356 --> 21:16.817
that the same thing happened to me,
then I lose all credibility.

21:16.900 --> 21:19.528
The whole story just gets picked apart.

21:19.611 --> 21:21.488
I could take the photos into Sex Crimes.

21:22.322 --> 21:23.907
