21:23.991 --> 21:27.619
Yeah, so some star-fucker cops
can get paid off to bury them? Yeah.

21:27.703 --> 21:29.913
I know the right people
to talk to, Delilah.

21:30.580 --> 21:31.623
Don't you trust me?

21:35.669 --> 21:36.503
Okay.

21:52.102 --> 21:55.647
Come on, people must have told you
you look like a model.

21:56.148 --> 21:58.525
-We should get a drink sometime.
-You're single?

21:59.067 --> 22:00.319
It's complicated.

22:00.610 --> 22:04.156
I'm going out of town tomorrow,
but I could take you out tonight.

22:04.239 --> 22:06.908
Tonight doesn't work,
but how about now?

22:06.992 --> 22:09.953
Seems like you've got
your hands full already.

22:13.123 --> 22:14.583
Oh, he's a big boy.

22:22.466 --> 22:24.134
I'm gonna need you to stay here for a bit.

22:24.718 --> 22:26.178
Read your book. I'll be back.

22:36.521 --> 22:38.774
-Don't go too short like last time, okay?
- I'm not.

22:39.399 --> 22:40.692
