22:43.362 --> 22:44.863
Top of the morning, will.i.am.

22:44.946 --> 22:46.073
I hope we didn't wake you.

22:46.156 --> 22:47.157
I hope we did.

22:47.991 --> 22:51.703
So I can apologize
for losing my shit yesterday.

22:52.704 --> 22:54.998
Oh, it's already forgotten.

22:55.624 --> 22:58.710
You are one magnanimous motherfucker.

22:59.086 --> 23:00.295
And we...

23:00.837 --> 23:02.672
are going to make a great team.

23:02.756 --> 23:05.926
