you would help him with his project.

23:06.218 --> 23:09.012
<i>-</i> <i>Only so I can have more of you.</i>
-Absolutely.

23:09.096 --> 23:10.347
Schweet.

23:10.430 --> 23:14.059
I had to push the Ted Hope meeting
because I was irate after...

23:14.559 --> 23:17.270
