23:17.604 --> 23:20.273
Uh, but It's fine. I'll pitch him
when he gets back from South By.

23:20.357 --> 23:21.608
Sounds like a plan.

23:21.691 --> 23:23.443
But you and I should get started
this afternoon.

23:23.735 --> 23:25.487
-Okay.
-Also, Lovey said something

23:25.570 --> 23:27.697
about all of us going
to the beach later today?

23:27.781 --> 23:28.740
Oh, right.

23:29.783 --> 23:31.326
<i> Sooner than I'd care to, but...</i>

23:31.410 --> 23:32.285
Great.

23:32.369 --> 23:33.829
But I need Love...

23:34.287 --> 23:36.706
to go with me
to buy a new suit for the pitch.

23:36.790 --> 23:38.458
Sure, let's go shopping.

23:38.542 --> 23:41.378
No, like, just me and Love.

23:42.254 --> 23:45.173
I get self-conscious
when I go suit shopping because of...

23:46.341 --> 23:47.342
my thighs.

23:48.802 --> 23:50.512
Forty, Will and I have plans.

23:51.847 --> 23:53.723
It's fine. Will doesn't mind.

23:54.891 --> 23:55.934
Do you, old sport?

23:57.602 --> 23:59.521
<i> Your brother is a monster.</i>

23:59.604 --> 24:00.439
Not at all.

24:02.232 --> 24:03.150
Happy shopping.

24:05.277 --> 24:08.738
<i> Becoming a better person</i>
<i>is way more aggravating than I thought,</i>

24:08.822 --> 24:11.241
<i>but I'm still going to find a way</i>
<i>to help your brother.</i>

24:12.075 --> 24:12.951
How's book one?

24:13.034 --> 24:16.538
Margarita just rescued the rape victim
from eternal damnation.

24:16.746 --> 24:19.499
So, uh,  you know... light beach reading.

24:25.213 --> 24:27.007
That's the book guy?

24:27.424 --> 24:28.800
He doesn't play for your team.

24:28.884 --> 24:32.012
