so why do you get all the hot zaddies?

24:32.262 --> 24:33.930
Okay, first,

24:34.014 --> 24:35.974
Will is like a eunuch to me.

24:36.391 --> 24:37.434
And Hendy?

24:37.517 --> 24:39.603
He is not my zaddy either.

24:39.686 --> 24:40.896
Which reminds me,

24:41.271 --> 24:42.856
I'm going to his screening tonight.

24:42.939 --> 24:45.859
Text me and invite me to sleep over
so D thinks I'm at your place.

24:45.942 --> 24:46.985
Thank you.

24:49.446 --> 24:52.324
<i> Why hasn't Delilah</i>
<i>gotten Henderson arrested yet?</i>

25:05.378 --> 25:07.047
<i> Flaming Hot Cheetos.</i>

25:07.130 --> 25:09.341
<i>Stress food, very bad sign.</i>

25:09.799 --> 25:11.927
Management should really get that fixed.

25:13.011 --> 25:14.513
What do you need, Apartment Three?

25:15.430 --> 25:18.350
Just wanted to make sure
you got that envelope on your doorstep.

25:20.060 --> 25:21.520
How did you know about that?

25:22.229 --> 25:23.939
I saw a girl drop it off.

25:24.940 --> 25:25.774
What'd she look like?

25:26.191 --> 25:28.693
I saw her from behind.
She had a... hoodie.

25:28.777 --> 25:29.611
Why?

25:31.404 --> 25:32.239
Nothing.

25:32.489 --> 25:34.115
Doesn't seem like nothing.

25:34.908 --> 25:36.243
Hey, is someone harassing you?

25:36.326 --> 25:37.244
No.

25:37.786 --> 25:41.248
Delilah, I've seen the look on your face.
If someone is bothering you, just--

25:42.666 --> 25:43.667
-Hi.
-Hi.

25:46.169 --> 25:48.630
If someone is bothering you,
go to the cops.

25:48.713 --> 25:51.007
-I'll go with you.
-Would you relax? Nobody's stalking me.

25:54.135 --> 25:55.428
This is about Henderson.

25:56.388 --> 25:59.808
The woman you saw dropped
his kiddie porn photos on my doorstep.

26:00.725 --> 26:02.102
Well, this is great, right?

26:02.352 --> 26:04.604
I showed 'em to a cop,
and he said they're useless

26:04.688 --> 26:07.107
and he can't do shit with them
because Henderson's not in them.

26:07.190 --> 26:09.234
And the backdrop's completely nondescript.

26:09.818 --> 26:10.902
Bastard's smart.

26:11.528 --> 26:14.406
-<i> Shit. Shit, shit, shit!</i>
-So what are you gonna do?

26:14.489 --> 26:17.033
Stick 'em in a drawer until somebody else
blows the whistle on him.

26:17.742 --> 26:20.829
If the police had found them on Henderson
or in Henderson's house,

26:20.912 --> 26:23.623
then they could've made a case,
but as it is...

26:24.583 --> 26:26.835
whoever swiped them
bungled the shit out of this.

26:33.925 --> 26:35.135
<i> Double fuck!</i>

26:35.218 --> 26:37.429
<i>Promised to help your brother,</i>
<i>but now I have to make sure</i>

26:37.512 --> 26:40.181
<i>Ellie doesn't</i>
<i>walk into the jaws of perversion.</i>

26:40.557 --> 26:42.183
<i>I'll have to keep it short with Forty.</i>

26:43.351 --> 26:44.185
Sit down.

26:44.811 --> 26:45.729
In the end,

26:46.146 --> 26:49.524
our guy has to murder all three women.

26:50.358 --> 26:52.736
It's like... the ultimate irony.

26:54.779 --> 26:55.739
So what do you think?

26:56.072 --> 26:58.908
<i> That it sounds like the most</i>
<i>anti-feminist horror film in history,</i>

26:58.992 --> 27:01.244
<i>-which is saying a lot.</i>
-I think it's really good.

27:01.328 --> 27:03.121
You don't think it gets wonky
in the middle?

27:03.204 --> 27:04.831
-No.
-You don't think we need to, like,

27:04.914 --> 27:07.125
spitball that page 90 shit?

27:07.417 --> 27:10.670
<i> He's not going to let me leave</i>
<i>until I say...</i>

27:10.754 --> 27:12.088
Honestly, I think it's genius.

27:14.299 --> 27:15.175
Okay...

27:15.675 --> 27:18.053
don't throw the G word around
if you don't mean it, Will.

27:18.428 --> 27:19.846
-I do.
-I knew it.

27:20.263 --> 27:23.183
Man, I wish I could go
to South By Pitch Fest tomorrow.

27:23.683 --> 27:24.684
It's fine.

27:24.768 --> 27:26.770
Gives us more time
to work the dough, right?

27:27.437 --> 27:28.772
I think we are on a roll.

27:28.855 --> 27:30.982
I think... we should go all night?

27:31.274 --> 27:34.611
<i> How do I get out now</i>
<i>without this six-foot-one baby</i>

27:34.694 --> 27:35.612
<i>throwing a tantrum?</i>

27:35.695 --> 27:38.239
No, no.
You don't want to overwork the dough.

27:38.323 --> 27:40.158
I think you should go to South By tonight.

27:40.700 --> 27:41.660
Pitch it tomorrow.

27:42.118 --> 27:43.787
-For reals?
-Take the red-eye.

27:44.287 --> 27:46.456
You said Ted Hope is there, right?

27:46.539 --> 27:47.999
Show him you're in demand.

27:48.208 --> 27:49.834
Start a bidding war.

27:51.336 --> 27:52.796
-Fuck yeah.
-Fuck yeah.

27:52.879 --> 27:54.589
-I'm gonna do it.
-Good for you.

28:01.930 --> 28:02.764
<i> Where you been?</i>

28:03.473 --> 28:04.599
At the market.

28:04.683 --> 28:05.850
For four hours?

28:05.975 --> 28:07.227
You should ask your son.

28:07.310 --> 28:09.729
He wanted to play hide-and-seek
and scare Mommy.

28:11.648 --> 28:13.441
I'm gonna get the rest of the groceries.

28:21.866 --> 28:23.785
You're old enough to know that your mom...

28:24.452 --> 28:27.539
sometimes accidentally tells a little lie.

28:28.164 --> 28:31.042
But I know you always tell the truth.

28:32.335 --> 28:33.211
Come here, Joey.

28:34.212 --> 28:35.171
Come here.

28:42.095 --> 28:44.556
Pain, it can make people truthful.

28:44.639 --> 28:45.515
Hey.

28:46.307 --> 28:47.642
What you doing with that rope?

28:48.518 --> 28:50.186
Don't worry, it's for Henderson.

28:51.479 --> 28:52.355
Uh-huh...

28:53.690 --> 28:57.068
And what exactly
are you planning to do to him?

28:58.027 --> 28:59.904
Gonna get him to confess on video,

29:00.447 --> 29:02.198
ruin his career, and get him arrested.

29:02.824 --> 29:04.451
Why? What'd you think I was gonna say?

29:06.202 --> 29:07.871
Someone else, not you...

29:09.205 --> 29:12.834
a less stable person might see...

29:13.501 --> 29:16.337
Hendy's depravity
as justification for killing him.

29:17.964 --> 29:19.007
That's not me.

29:20.717 --> 29:21.593
I know.

29:22.469 --> 29:23.720
I know it's not.

29:24.763 --> 29:27.557
You're thoughtful, controlled...

29:30.310 --> 29:31.519
The more I learn about you,

29:31.603 --> 29:34.105
the more clearly I see
the answer to your question.

29:34.647 --> 29:35.857
How can you...

29:36.357 --> 29:39.778
be sure I'll be loyal once you let me out?

29:40.653 --> 29:41.696
The answer is...

29:43.782 --> 29:45.033
there is no answer.

29:45.575 --> 29:48.369
No matter what I say, you will never
be sure if I'll turn you in.

29:48.453 --> 29:51.331
<i> But I need to be sure, Love, for us.</i>

29:51.414 --> 29:52.373
Hold on.

29:53.041 --> 29:55.752
I know you want to do the right thing

29:55.835 --> 29:58.171
or you wouldn't have asked at all.

29:58.755 --> 30:02.175
I've done business with bad people,
you're not them.

30:02.842 --> 30:03.676
You...

30:04.260 --> 30:06.596
do bad things when you feel trapped

30:07.138 --> 30:10.183
or, key, to protect someone, which...

30:10.725 --> 30:13.603
we all hope we would have the courage
to do that.

30:14.521 --> 30:16.606
To me, that makes you more good than bad.

30:17.816 --> 30:19.442
I think you're a good man.

30:20.902 --> 30:22.028
You could kill Henderson,

30:22.111 --> 30:24.572
but you're letting justice
take its course.

30:25.657 --> 30:27.075
That's what a good man would do.

30:27.158 --> 30:29.702
<i> He's biased, but I hope he's right.</i>

30:30.078 --> 30:32.705
But to really be good, Joe,

30:32.789 --> 30:34.374
you have to let me out of here.

30:35.333 --> 30:37.460
<i> Another impossible puzzle, Love,</i>

30:37.544 --> 30:40.004
<i>but for you, I'll try to solve anything.</i>

30:45.426 --> 30:48.179
<i> It's not the best time,</i>
<i>but you always come first.</i>

30:48.263 --> 30:49.097
Hey, you.

30:49.347 --> 30:52.433
Did you tell Forty
to take a red-eye to South By?

30:53.226 --> 30:54.435
I may have mentioned it, yeah.

30:54.519 --> 30:58.147
I really wish you would have asked me.
Film fests are tough on his sobriety.

30:58.231 --> 30:59.732
I didn't realize that, I'm sorry.

30:59.816 --> 31:02.235
I appreciate that,
but it still feels weird,

31:02.318 --> 31:04.070
like you were trying
to get him out of town

31:04.153 --> 31:05.989
so that you wouldn't have
to deal with him.

31:06.072 --> 31:08.950
<i> Being attracted to very smart women</i>
<i>is a double-edged sword.</i>

31:09.033 --> 31:11.744
-I would never do that.
<i>-He said you used the words "bidding war."</i>

31:11.828 --> 31:12.954
<i> I should lie.</i>

31:13.162 --> 31:16.291
<i>Half-truths just end up getting me burned</i>
<i>so I should lie.</i>

31:16.374 --> 31:18.459
Will, please do not make this worse
by lying to me.

31:18.543 --> 31:20.712
<i> I have to because I can't tell you</i>
<i>the whole truth,</i>

31:20.795 --> 31:23.006
<i>which happens to be I did it</i>
<i>to save someone helpless.</i>

31:23.089 --> 31:24.924
<i>Speaking of, need to stop her, now.</i>

31:25.383 --> 31:26.634
<i> Hello? Are you there?</i>

31:26.718 --> 31:28.553
<i> Yeah, I'm-- I'm here. I'm here.</i>

31:29.762 --> 31:30.930
You're right.

31:31.014 --> 31:32.640
<i>I just wasn't thinking. I messed up.</i>

31:32.724 --> 31:35.268
And from now on, I'll do better.

31:35.560 --> 31:36.561
I promise.

31:37.228 --> 31:38.771
That is what I needed to hear.

31:38.855 --> 31:40.982
<i>Now I have to go.</i>
<i>I don't want to miss my flight.</i>

31:41.858 --> 31:42.775
-Your flight?
<i>-Yeah.</i>

31:42.859 --> 31:45.612
I'm going to be Forty's sober companion
at South By.

31:46.613 --> 31:49.240
<i> Kill me now.</i>
<i>Kill Forty, kill everything.</i>

31:49.324 --> 31:51.200
-Have a great trip.
<i>-Call you from Austin.</i>

31:51.618 --> 31:54.829
<i> Perfect. Now I have to get Ellie out</i>
<i>of Henderson's, then get his confession.</i>

31:54.913 --> 31:56.122
<i>I'm not sure how to do either.</i>

31:56.205 --> 31:57.540
<i>What could go wrong?</i>

32:03.755 --> 32:05.632
-@Ellie-Eyeballs, hey.
-Hey.

32:05.715 --> 32:08.092
So bad news.
Jonah's girl came down with the flu

32:08.176 --> 32:10.094
and Jonah's the one with the print,

32:10.470 --> 32:12.096
so no screening tonight. Sorry.

32:12.388 --> 32:13.973
Here, I'll call you an Uber.

32:14.057 --> 32:15.475
Wait, dude, I came all this way.

32:16.184 --> 32:17.477
We can still hang.

32:17.727 --> 32:18.937
I can show you my short.

32:19.520 --> 32:20.980
It's still in progress, but--

32:21.064 --> 32:23.316
Listen, we're friends and it's cool.

32:23.399 --> 32:25.276
I mean, you're massively cool, but...

32:26.152 --> 32:27.278
you're also 15,

32:27.362 --> 32:29.656
so we're not hanging out
in my house alone.

32:31.407 --> 32:32.825
<i> What is his game here?</i>

32:32.909 --> 32:34.285
Okay, neurotic.

32:34.661 --> 32:37.163
I'm not some random girl child.

32:37.246 --> 32:39.290
And you said for weeks
you would watch my short.

32:40.124 --> 32:40.959
All right, fine.

32:41.042 --> 32:42.919
But you have to promise me
you won't tell anybody

32:43.002 --> 32:45.296
that you were here alone with me, okay?
'Cause it's kinda--

32:45.380 --> 32:46.255
I get it.

32:46.339 --> 32:48.299
I'm a vault. Scout's honor.

32:48.883 --> 32:52.720
<i> Oh, this is his clever trick</i>
<i>to make her feel safe,</i>

32:52.804 --> 32:54.472
<i>like she chose.</i>

33:13.825 --> 33:15.368
-You're a filmmaker.

33:15.785 --> 33:18.579
I saw some <i>Rear Window</i>
and a little bit of...

33:19.122 --> 33:21.374
<i>Florida Project,</i> but with your own pathos.

33:22.250 --> 33:24.752
